#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:2
msgid "GENERATED"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:4
msgid "Is this source file generated as part of the build or CMake process."
msgstr "此來源檔案是否為建置或 CMake 過程的一部分所產生。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:6
msgid ""
"Turning on the ``GENERATED`` source file property in one directory allows "
"the associated source file to be used across directories without the need to "
"manually setting that property for other directory scopes, too. "
"Additionally, it may now be set only to boolean values, and may not be "
"turned off once turned on.  See policy :policy:`CMP0118`."
msgstr ""
"在一個目錄中開啟 ``GENERATED`` 來源檔案屬性允許關聯的來源檔案跨目錄使用，無需"
"手動為其他目錄範圍設定該屬性。此外，它現在只能設定為布林值，且一旦開啟就不能"
"關閉。請參閱政策 :policy:`CMP0118`。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:13
msgid ""
"Whether or not a source file is generated is an all-or-nothing global "
"property of the source.  Consequently, the ``GENERATED`` source file "
"property is now visible in all directories.  See policy :policy:`CMP0163`."
msgstr ""
"來源檔案是否為產生的是一個全有全無的全域屬性。因此，``GENERATED`` 來源檔案屬"
"性現在在所有目錄中都可見。請參閱政策 :policy:`CMP0163`。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:18
msgid ""
"Tells the internal CMake engine that a source file is generated by an "
"outside process such as another build step, or the execution of CMake "
"itself. This information is then used to exempt the file from any existence "
"or validity checks."
msgstr ""
"告訴內部 CMake 引擎，來源檔案是由外部過程（例如另一個建置步驟或 CMake 本身的"
"執行）產生的。然後此資訊用於免除該檔案的任何存在性或有效性檢查。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:23
msgid "Any file that is"
msgstr "任何符合以下條件的檔案"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:25
msgid ""
"created by the execution of commands such as :command:`add_custom_command` "
"which run during the build"
msgstr "由在建置期間執行的命令（例如 :command:`add_custom_command`）所建立"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:27
msgid ""
"listed as one of the ``BYPRODUCTS`` of an :command:`add_custom_command` or :"
"command:`add_custom_target` command, or"
msgstr ""
"被列為 :command:`add_custom_command` 或 :command:`add_custom_target` 命令的 "
"``BYPRODUCTS`` 之一，或"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:29
msgid ""
"created by a CMake ``AUTOGEN`` operation such as :prop_tgt:`AUTOMOC`, :"
"prop_tgt:`AUTORCC`, or :prop_tgt:`AUTOUIC`"
msgstr ""
"由 CMake 的 ``AUTOGEN`` 操作（例如 :prop_tgt:`AUTOMOC`、:prop_tgt:`AUTORCC` "
"或 :prop_tgt:`AUTOUIC`）所建立"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:32
msgid "will be marked with the ``GENERATED`` property."
msgstr "都將被標記為 ``GENERATED`` 屬性。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:34
msgid ""
"When a generated file created as the ``OUTPUT`` of an :command:"
"`add_custom_command` command is explicitly listed as a source file for any "
"target in the same directory scope (which usually means the same "
"``CMakeLists.txt`` file), CMake will automatically create a dependency to "
"make sure the file is generated before building that target."
msgstr ""
"當作為 :command:`add_custom_command` 命令的 ``OUTPUT`` 建立的產生檔案被明確列"
"為相同目錄範圍（通常表示同一個 ``CMakeLists.txt`` 檔案）內任何目標的來源檔案"
"時，CMake 會自動建立一個依賴關係，以確保在建置該目標之前產生該檔案。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:40
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Makefile Generators` will remove ``GENERATED`` files during ``make "
"clean``."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Makefile Generators` 將在 ``make clean`` 期間移除 ``GENERATED`` 檔案。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/GENERATED.rst:43
msgid ""
"Generated sources may be hidden in some IDE tools, while in others they "
"might be shown. For the special case of sources generated by CMake's :"
"prop_tgt:`AUTOMOC`, :prop_tgt:`AUTORCC` or :prop_tgt:`AUTOUIC` "
"functionality, the :prop_gbl:`AUTOGEN_SOURCE_GROUP`, :prop_gbl:"
"`AUTOMOC_SOURCE_GROUP`, :prop_gbl:`AUTORCC_SOURCE_GROUP` and :prop_gbl:"
"`AUTOUIC_SOURCE_GROUP` target properties may influence where the generated "
"sources are grouped in the project's file lists."
msgstr ""
"產生的來源可能會在某些 IDE 工具中隱藏，而在其他 IDE 中則可能顯示。對於 CMake "
"的 :prop_tgt:`AUTOMOC`、:prop_tgt:`AUTORCC` 或 :prop_tgt:`AUTOUIC` 功能所產生"
"的來源的特殊情況，:prop_gbl:`AUTOGEN_SOURCE_GROUP`、:prop_gbl:"
"`AUTOMOC_SOURCE_GROUP`、:prop_gbl:`AUTORCC_SOURCE_GROUP` 和 :prop_gbl:"
"`AUTOUIC_SOURCE_GROUP` 目標屬性可能會影響產生的來源在專案檔案清單中的分組位"
"置。"
